{"tid":1759430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"預測明日理大情況：明搜證，暗搜捕","createTime":"2019-11-27T15:44:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T16:30:35.000Z","uid":113155,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fa2b0e40eeb9a08cd1b87ba1f6ebe8cc2302e2c7","tid":1759430,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:44:34.000Z","msg":"狗一定唔夠僵光明正大攻入去，睇下嗰日全世界影到佢攻入a core，警慌會都唔敢認，矢口否認入過去就知。<br />\n大學係好撚大穫，人權法極速過大家有眼睇，區選大家有眼睇。<br />\n聽日，只不過係狗備自己一個落台階撤姐。<br />\n<br />\n明：真係搜證，唔會搜捕<br />\n暗：臥底一早掌握學生足跡，只會事後跟蹤搜捕<br />\n<br />\n我哋可以做啲咩？<br />\n1、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呼籲大量記者聽日影撚住佢哋</span></span>，就算入唔到去影住，要各大門口守住，影住佢哋出番黎。<br />\n<br />\n2、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">清潔校園你我有責！萬人清潔理大</span></span><br />\n一解封即刻清潔校園，入邊咁污糟，淺色衫容易有跡洗唔甩，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要着深色衫，最好黑色啦</span></span>。山埃二噁英遍佈校園，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要帶番個口罩</span></span>。清潔後一定汗流浹背，一定要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">帶多套衫，借備朋友換都好</span></span>。<br />\nSem break學生要勤力啲清潔啦，番工放工後好去啦。<br />\n<br />\n手足，你哋唔撚洗驚，狗已經冇棋行，好快你哋可以呼吸到新鮮空氣。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保護好自己，影相寫不自殺，腥備親朋戚友，一撚定要做！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到⋯⋯"},{"pid":"9e7ba47511dbf50a83fab92c3195efdb17141ae9","tid":1759430,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n前線狗冇腦姐，啲白狗唔係真係無腦，攻大學好大機係前線狗不受控"},{"pid":"86b3b77e88e8df1669ff5afc81efe6b44e31956a","tid":1759430,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:46:03.000Z","msg":"保護自己，唔好被消失"},{"pid":"e4d558150af2b744726e243974ac13c3d5503d35","tid":1759430,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:47:28.000Z","msg":"手足一定要好好保護自己<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣傳一下個APP<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a>"},{"pid":"62921bca0fea1cdd00138d02e7609135db826956","tid":1759430,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:49:38.000Z","msg":"屌，啱睇寶寶channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2315 #理大 理大寶寶開記招<br />\n<br />\n講述有卧底同疑似黑社會入內騷擾佢地半夜三更凌晨十二點至六點 狂敲門唔俾寶寶們瞓，又會爆寶寶門，同埋著晒gear 蒙面扮FA叫寶寶走<br />\n所以寶寶們無得休息要到朝早六點後先天訓<br />\n擔心已有寶寶被消失帶走<br />\n<br />\n咩都唔撚驚，最撚驚你哋被消失！"},{"pid":"f2e7dede9e7a4b1adf7a8146b53df7c768f18e41","tid":1759430,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:50:22.000Z","msg":"呼籲手足，影相寫不自殺聲明腥備親朋戚友！<br />\n求下你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2610fc660c93cead229141759390eed7f43920d1","tid":1759430,"uid":69202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:51:25.000Z","msg":"好同意"},{"pid":"459acca7eee88cce4af7f150cf82dcb722208531","tid":1759430,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139c80aa75497526fdbb12952ee5e2727cd6d42d","tid":1759430,"uid":274723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62921bca0fea1cdd00138d02e7609135db826956","tid":1759430,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:49:38.000Z","msg":"屌，啱睇寶寶channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2315 #理大 理大寶寶開記招<br />\n<br />\n講述有卧底同疑似黑社會入內騷擾佢地半夜三更凌晨十二點至六點 狂敲門唔俾寶寶們瞓，又會